Termux method 


#1. Install Tor
$ pkg install tor

#2. Clone the GitHub Repository
$ git clone https://github.com/mahito-hacker/Auto-Tor

#3.  Navigate into the cloned directory
$ cd Auto-Tor

#4.  Install the requirements 
$ pip install -r requirements.txt

#5. Open Tor in a Background Process
$ tor -f ~/.tor/torrc &

#6. Run the aut.py Script in new tab
$ python3 aut.py




Linux method 


#1. Install Tor
$ sudo apt install tor

#2. Clone the GitHub Repository
$ git clone https://github.com/Moto-sudo/Auto-Tor.git

#3. Navigate into the Cloned Directory
$ cd Auto-Tor

#4. Install Python Requirements
$ pip install -r requirements.txt

#5. Open Tor in a Background Process
$ tor -f ~/.tor/torrc &

#6. Run the aut.py Script in new tab
$ python3 aut.py

